                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-58-off345 t18130714-58-cd346"></join>, a saddle, value 1 l. a bridle, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130714-58-victim633" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin 
                     Travers
                  <interp inst="t18130714-58-victim633" type="surname" value="Travers"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-58-victim633" type="given" value="Benjamin"></interp>
